{"tid":2027174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現好多人唔識玩過三關","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T19:59:48.000Z","uid":208834,"like":68,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c08d2a62e05a4d94bba42a480bd91dc7a19343bb","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"黑暗前夕 同大家分享點玩過三關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般人玩過三關 先手一定係拎中間嗰格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因經驗話我哋知 呢個位去贏係恆之有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果你點都拎唔到嗰中間格<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解一定要強求中間嗰格呢？<br />\n仲有其他8格都有機會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在好多人 心入面得中間嗰格(i.e.勇武)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋其實好聰明 因為佢哋知全面行呢步已經贏咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢班人同時又好蠢 中間以外一律唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對手就比我哋聰明得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理有冇用 乜都要咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n35+討論有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  谷盡的票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非又有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  行過路落都拉 嚇走佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  阻住佢做生意 日日用傳媒屌尻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際線有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  鎖網我都在所不惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想講今後言論自由將會愈縮愈窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用時間來互屌去討論有用定冇用 成效高定低 唔係理想方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預期討論到乜都做唔到決定<br />\n不如試下:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我要曬</strong></span><br />\n咩方法 有冇效 但凡你想同我爭 都盡全力唔放比你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你永遠唔知邊格先可以帶比你勝利<br />\n<br />\n最後，各位保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef5656ee1e5d139a41d2b62c99438af5b925b4f","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beddc98aca9603ce5092f020048b89bb87bee8d7","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5679567c83e56829e801111c16412513a7318dc5","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749a944add2cbcf6e6c2774d1267981acd9dbcc6","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97d8f3625f134b5d11676ea43c171b1f0e6a173","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887614bb8b113fb4fbd338f29612425a55e604bc","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,