0-05-21T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"[off topic]其實第一步應該行角位<br />\n計埋symmetry之後唔係好多個case<br />\n試下就知"},{"pid":"a3fc8b2f122124d6a19e214a61dc3d648d289f6d","tid":2027174,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"一向都覺得咩都要做，並唔係我要贏晒，而係要對家打擊我地果時做錯野"},{"pid":"63a93b0d3d174c52398600f8562754b69a037244","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512268febc4f9485cc288bbedd3574e412970696","tid":2027174,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c08d2a62e05a4d94bba42a480bd91dc7a19343bb","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"黑暗前夕 同大家分享點玩過三關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般人玩過三關 先手一定係拎中間嗰格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因經驗話我哋知 呢個位去贏係恆之有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係如果你點都拎唔到嗰中間格<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解一定要強求中間嗰格呢？<br />\n仲有其他8格都有機會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在好多人 心入面得中間嗰格(i.e.勇武)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋其實好聰明 因為佢哋知全面行呢步已經贏咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢班人同時又好蠢 中間以外一律唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對手就比我哋聰明得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理有冇用 乜都要咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n35+討論有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  谷盡的票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非又有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  行過路落都拉 嚇走佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  阻住佢做生意 日日用傳媒屌尻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際線有冇用？ <br />\n對手:唔理有冇用 盡全力阻止  鎖網我都在所不惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想講今後言論自由將會愈縮愈窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用時間來互屌去討論有用定冇用 成效高定低 唔係理想方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預期討論到乜都做唔到決定<br />\n不如試下:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我要曬</strong></span><br />\n咩方法 有冇效 但凡你想同我爭 都盡全力唔放比你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你永遠唔知邊格先可以帶比你勝利<br />\n<br />\n最後，各位保重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"[off topic]其實第一步應該行角位<br />\n計埋symmetry之後唔係好多個case<br />\n試下就知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"利申唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有時以為係最好嘅都未必係唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d292507bc0d06627fbb2ba07446995c1e6e56e7b","tid":2027174,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"咁我先手搶中，你後手贏比我睇，ok?"},{"pid":"3d357603dbfb9dba6465515aceaee1a06f73f479","tid":2027174,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYGEnF8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYGEnF8.gif&h=1279b76e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f93d393d0ac95237279ecd181a67cb66e7ad4247","tid":2027174,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited