ormal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有冇腦架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"贏到就得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係知你一諗 時間一過 就到返對手行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘最後一格都冇就比人贏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加對家行使橫手要中間嗰格㗎啦<br />\n開咗個頭唔通投降唔玩咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"哦，原來有限時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />doFF完未"},{"pid":"37d16218728fca5b345890c3f8eb1cd6c1ad11ed","tid":2027174,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"你講既野全部都有一個前設<br />\n就係動員力同軍心都無限大<br />\n詳見之前區選 連登吹風勇武行動要「讓路」比選舉<br />\n結果行動派就因為各種原因沉寂左一段好長既時間<br />\n對家就爭取時間諗策略同上門拉手足<br />\n你既諗法係 反正贏同輸 其他野都可以照做 <br />\n點解唔贏多瓣？<br />\n但問題係 你有無咁強既動員能力？<br />\n你能唔能夠確定每件事可以獨立進行？<br />\n你撥人手去一件事上面<br />\n即使 退一步講 比你贏左<br />\n帳面上贏左既成功感會唔會令一部分人想靜觀其變<br />\n而前題係我地一早知吹雞做果件事效果有限？<br />\n淨係Time Cost已經係一個問題<br />\n樣樣野都試係會增加成本的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3185f2e341467b13384d6429b6cec9f89fbd84a","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d995b88e067cf13484ee01704d7c4b80e43c017","tid":2027174,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2a54b8a5d3cfebf0961187a60819f73a88eae3","tid":2027174,"uid":208834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86589e73d9731754a41799fc389d5131d6202ac0","tid":2027174,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"叫我比多幾格你行？咁咪即係lur地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有冇腦架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"贏到就得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係知你一諗 時間一過 就到返對手行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi